      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DOONGALLA GHOST (1) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (30.91) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Form at the trip sound including three wins. Can atone. HURRICANE MIST (8) was in the minors two back (30.57) at this track but ran below best last time there, finishing 6th. Solid record here at the distance winning six races. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. In the mix. BIT OF POTASH (6) did a good job to finish third last time out over 460m at Geelong (26.54) in a Rank Limit - Grade 5, the second top-three finish on the trot. Key player on best and worth another try. NO MORE EXTRAS (2) cannot be underestimated.",
